  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink201">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l>aṉṉāy vāḻivēṇ ṭaṉṉai yeṉṉai</l>
          <l>tāṉu malaintā ṉemakkuṉ taḻaiyāyiṉa</l>
          <l>poṉvī maṇiyarum piṉavē</l>
          <l>yeṉṉa maraṅkolavar cāra lavvē</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation">
          <l>Oh Mother, please Mother, </l>
          <l>that which my lord himself wore</l> 
          <l>and which [also] became the foliage for me,</l> 
          <l>had golden mature-blossoms and sapphire buds.</l> 
          <l>What are the trees upon his mountain slope?</l> 

        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
